{"type": "article", "id": 51364, "title": "可口可乐又出联名款，周杰伦成为帝舵全球代言人 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-03-22T04:05:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29160, "name": "私募"}, {"id": 330, "name": "可口可乐"}, {"id": 25621, "name": "KKR"}, {"id": 738, "name": "麦当劳"}, {"id": 5146, "name": "周杰伦"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180322105639Lkix5l9RnXuCJa6r.png", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-2-43813.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>周杰伦成为帝舵品牌全球代言人</b></a>，诠释帝舵表“天生敢为”的品牌精神。帝舵此前的全球代言人是贝克汉姆。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322114636qij38GIOHaVvfEPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26334.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>PEACEBIRD MEN X Coca-Cola 推出合作系列</b></a>，延续了可口可乐经典的 LOGO 字体设计，使用标志性红白色的对比碰撞。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322104416qt0Wj9D7LPdn6i1a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.764381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的 Case</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26349.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>H&amp;M 发布春季大片</b></a>，《剪刀手爱德华》女主 Winona Ryder 和《复仇者联盟》中的绯红女巫 Elizabeth Olsen 出演。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe src=\"http://open.iqiyi.com/developer/player_js/coopPlayerIndex.html?vid=4f7cc0519a9a78e0251f4c4566707f03&amp;tvId=969258800&amp;accessToken=2.f22860a2479ad60d8da7697274de9346&amp;appKey=3955c3425820435e86d0f4cdfe56f5e7&amp;appId=1368&amp;height=100%&amp;width=100%\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/43809\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳推出“鸡粥物语”的粥碗</b></a>。喝完粥之后，碗底会露出一句亲密俳句。麦当劳在今年 1 月更新了三款早餐粥，“粥王系列”号称请教了香港、深圳、宁波三大粥王。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322115059AeZkVF5bLm0Kxsup.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322115108SzcOPpA4oG9uaYhU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322115114wTAuhtHBNMe4XIiz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24258.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">为推广现磨咖啡业务</a></b>，7 - Eleven 品牌 CITY CAFE 与桂纶美在樱花季推出了这支广告片《樱花七日篇》。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=c0604l33e8s&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26339.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为推广新品全面屏手机 R15</b></a>，OPPO 发布了 3 支 10 秒创意动画，呈现全面屏在拍照、玩游戏、看视频时能够带来的无拘束体验。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322105058KJV5gTjNhLeDvU0i.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.697842\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/03/21/kkr-launches-one-stop-digital-marketing-company-cue-co/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>私募投资机构 KKR&nbsp; 也做起了广告生意</b></a><strong>，</strong>宣布为中国市场成立一站式数字营销机构开域集团（Cue &amp; Co.）。KKR 的投资将联合齐欣互动、安与吉、赢之嘉和赢纳科技四家公司，共同打造具有广泛营销服务能力的多品牌公司。<br></p><p>题图来源：数英网</p><style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 24.0px; font: 18.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #4d4f53; -webkit-text-stroke: #4d4f53; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 24.0px; font: 14.0px 'PingFang SC Semibold'; color: #282828; -webkit-text-stroke: #282828} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 14.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>"}